Package: empichar
Type: Package
Title: Evaluates the empirical characteristic function for multivariate samples
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Guillermo", "Basulto-Elias", email = "guillermobasulto@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Guillermo Basulto-Elias <guillermobasulto@gmail.com>
Description: Evaluate the empirical characteristic function of univariate and multivariate samples.
    This package uses RcppArmadillo for fast evaluation. It is also possible to export the code to be used in other packages at C++ level.
